              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          );
        })}
      </div>

      {/* Smaller cards: Card headings General Sans 700 */}
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        {[
          { title: "The Right Guidance Matters", quote: "I was confused about choosing a course, but TESCA helped me find the perfect pathway for my career goals.", author: "Simranjeet Kaur" },
          { title: "From Dream To Departure", quote: "The counsellors were supportive throughout the journey. Today I'm studying at my dream university abroad.", author: "Rahul Sharma" },
